high_descs: walk to face counter behind sink
pick up butter knife from under sponge on counter
walk to face counter to left of stove
put knife into green cup on the left on the counter
pick up the green cup from counter
turn to face the kitchen sink
put green cup into sink basin
anns.task_desc: put green cup and knife into sink basin

high_descs: Turn right, hang a left at the wall and walk to the counter on the left.
Pick up the knife under the green sponge on the counter.
Turn around, hang a right at the wall, turn right towards the fridge, turn right and walk to the counter on the left.
Put the knife inside the green glass in front of the spatula in the middle of the counter.
Pick up the green glass with the knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Put the glass with the knife inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a glass with a knife in a sink.

high_descs: Turn right to move around the island to stand facing the counter and centered between the two chairs.
Pick up the butter knife from beneath the sponge.
Turn left to move around to the other side of the island and stop facing the counter above the dishwasher.
Place the knife in the green cup closest to the wall behind the counter.
Pick up the cup with the knife in it from the counter.
Turn around and face the sink.
Place the cup with the knife inside in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move a knife in a cup to the sink.
